address.streetAddress: Mary Lou Plan, Ivy at Tesoro Viejo

location.fullValue: Mary Lou Plan, Ivy at Tesoro Viejo

data.description: This DR Horton home with breathtaking views of a natural preserve and the Sierra Mountains, offers you the beauty of nature in your expansive backyard, free from rear neighbors. Meticulously renovated in 2022 with more than $150K in upgrades, this home surpasses the standard of a model home. Enter into a stylish interior adorned with quartz countertops, custom tile, smart automation, and waterproof wood-look flooring. The open-concept Kitchen boasts KitchenAid gas appliances, undercabinet lighting, and an elegant marble backsplash. The Great Room, featuring a large slider and a gas fireplace, seamlessly extends to an expansive California room perfect for hosting gatherings. With ample storage, this home offers the versatility of an office and an extended loft that could serve as a fourth bedroom. The Primary Suite is complemented by a tastefully designed bathroom. Convenience is key, with proximity to amenities and a school just across the street. This residence effortlessly blends modern luxury with awe-inspiring surroundings. Welcome to the pinnacle of sophisticated living at Tesoro Viejo. (All appliances and first floor furniture are negotiable, Solar is owned, HOA includes Wifi).
